## üß† Introduction
This document provides intermediate-level knowledge for AI learners who have completed the basics. It covers fundamental machine learning and deep learning techniques, algorithms, and essential AI engineering skills required to build practical AI applications.

---

## üî• Core Topics
### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Machine Learning Foundations
- **Supervised Learning**: Regression, Classification
- **Unsupervised Learning**: Clustering, Anomaly Detection
- **Reinforcement Learning**: Q-Learning, Deep Q-Networks (DQN)
- **Model Evaluation**: Precision, Recall, F1-score, ROC-AUC
- **Hyperparameter Tuning**: Grid Search, Random Search, Bayesian Optimization
- **Feature Engineering**: PCA, Feature Scaling, Encoding Techniques

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Deep Learning & Neural Networks
- **Feedforward Neural Networks (FNNs)**
- **Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) for Image Processing**
- **Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) for Sequence Data**
- **Transformers & Attention Mechanisms**
- **Autoencoders & Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs)**
- **Optimization Algorithms**: Adam, RMSprop, SGD
- **Activation Functions**: ReLU, Leaky ReLU, Sigmoid, Tanh

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Data Handling & Processing
- **Data Preprocessing & Cleaning** (Handling Missing Data, Outlier Detection)
- **Feature Extraction**: TF-IDF, Word2Vec, FastText, BERT Embeddings
- **Dimensionality Reduction**: PCA, t-SNE, UMAP
- **Data Augmentation for Deep Learning**

### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Advanced AI Engineering Concepts
- **AI Model Deployment**: Flask, FastAPI, Docker, Kubernetes
- **MLOps & Model Monitoring**: MLflow, TensorFlow Serving, TorchServe
- **Scalability & Performance Optimization**
- **AutoML & Automated Feature Engineering**
- **AI Ethics & Bias Mitigation**

### 5Ô∏è‚É£ Practical AI Applications
- **Natural Language Processing (NLP)**: Sentiment Analysis, Text Classification, Named Entity Recognition (NER)
- **Computer Vision**: Image Classification, Object Detection, Image Segmentation
- **AI in Cybersecurity**: Threat Detection, Fraud Prevention
- **AI in Healthcare**: Disease Prediction, Medical Image Analysis
- **AI in Finance**: Stock Market Prediction, Risk Assessment

